<span id="freeTextContainer14575272504763553884">It was one of my required readings in college. <br/><br/>Like every Malamud novel, <i>The Fixer</i> is a very disturbing read, almost traumatic. <br/>The writing is brilliant, but I have no intention to read it again. Ever.</span>

