		<td>
		    <b>
          <a title="Literary Award Winners Fiction Book Club" class="actionLink" href="https://www.goodreads.com/topic/show/19153150-the-fixer-by-bernard-malamud-pages-1---150">Literary Award Wi...:</a>
        </b>
      
			<a class="actionLink" href="/topic/show/19153150-the-fixer-by-bernard-malamud-pages-1---150">The Fixer by Bernard Malamud, pages 1 - 150</a>
		</td>
		<td class="nobreak">
		  4
		  
